Package com.emc.atmos.api.request

Interface Summary
ContentRequest Represents a request that has content to send in the request body.
 

Class Summary
CreateAccessTokenRequest Represents a request to create an anonymous access token.
CreateObjectRequest Represents a create object request.
CreateSubtenantRequest Represents a request to create a new Atmos Subtenant in EMC ViPR.
ListAccessTokensRequest Represents a request to list all access tokens owned by the UID
ListDirectoryRequest Represents a request to list all of the object under a directory in the subtenant namespace.
ListMetadataRequest<T extends ListMetadataRequest<T>> Represents common elements of list requests that may include object metadata.
ListObjectsRequest Represents a request to list/query the objects of a specific listable metadata name (tag).
ListRequest<T extends ListRequest<T>> Common elements of a request for a list of items.
ListVersionsRequest Represents a request to list the versions of an object.
ObjectRequest<T extends ObjectRequest<T>> Represents an Atmos REST request dealing with a specific object.
PreSignedRequest Represents a request that has been pre-signed and is valid until expiration.
PutObjectRequest<T extends PutObjectRequest<T>> Represents a write object request (create or update).
ReadObjectRequest Represents an Atmos read-object request.
Request Represents an Atmos REST request.
UpdateObjectRequest Represents an update object request.
